    public class GraphXPrimitiveKeyOpenHashMap<K,V>
extends Object
implements scala.collection.Iterable<scala.Tuple2<K,V>>, scala.Serializable
    A fast hash map implementation for primitive, non-null keys. This hash map supports insertions and updates, but not deletions. This map is about an order of magnitude faster than java.util.HashMap, while using much less space overhead.

    Under the hood, it uses our OpenHashSet implementation.
